WEBVTT

00:00:01.028 --> 00:00:03.920
My name is Rebecca, and I'm a cyborg.

00:00:03.944 --> 00:00:06.968
(Laughter)

00:00:06.992 --> 00:00:11.206
Specifically, I have 32
computer chips inside my head,

00:00:11.230 --> 00:00:13.495
which rebuild my sense of hearing.

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:15.871
This is called a cochlear implant.

00:00:16.805 --> 00:00:19.885
You remember the Borg from Star Trek,

00:00:19.909 --> 00:00:24.004
those aliens who conquered and absorbed
everything in sight?

00:00:24.958 --> 00:00:26.139
Well, that's me.

00:00:26.163 --> 00:00:27.805
(Laughter)

00:00:27.829 --> 00:00:30.543
The good news is
I come for your technology